Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost at the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana!
