Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.44,0:02:21.45,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,0)\be1}One-Night Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll have to cross it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't gonna hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you from around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This bridge isn't going to last.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to cross it again when I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right. I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who this person is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming out so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter, Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell from the Kazura Bridge three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately she survived, but all she\Ndoes now is sit under the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had quite a few doctors look at her,\Nbut she doesn't have any head injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Hana doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that did this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Do something for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take me to the bottom of the gorge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And... tell me what happened\Nwhen Hana fell to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't refuse a marriage arrangement\Nwith the head family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we wouldn't receive any more\Nsupport in this village if you refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My family would get ostracized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents should too, if they really care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't live the life you want to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go past the gulf, past the mountains\Nto somewhere open and bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do that, Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, it's a bit weak there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't abandon everyone just\Nso that we can live as we please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll always think of me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always think of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I have to hide my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's just cross the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell from a fatal height.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet she walked home on her own legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But... she became hollow inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone cried saying that she'd become a "Tanimodori".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tanimodori"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Such people appear every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They fall into the valley and come out\Nalive, but their minds are consumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:20.47,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Hitoyobashi: One-Night Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They die on the night when the "Hitoyobashi" shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hitoyobashi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,People have seen a bridge spanning\Nacross the valley for just one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a while ago though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing that are possessing Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana? Possessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By a vine-like Mushi called a Nisekazura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not easy to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rather frail for a Nisekazura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like it's said in the scriptures, they're\Nstrong when you tug the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already getting dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all rushing toward the remaining sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There isn't enough light here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got bad news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither the "Tanimodori" nor the\N"Hitoyobashi" are legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Both can be explained by Nisekazura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, Nisekazura live on treetops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nisekazura here must be trying to flee\Nfrom the gulf by taking over other beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They need more light, but they don't have\Nthe energy to climb to the top of the gulf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, they live in another being's body,\Ngathering sunlight and strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When enough have gathered, they leave\Nin swarms to head to better places.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the "Hitoyobashi".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's a migration of Mushi across\Na valley every twenty or so years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, why do the "Tanimodori" die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't they be cured once the\NMushi or whatever leaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked around, but I didn't see any animal skeletons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nisekazura are most likely infecting onto corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case, even if they leave, they'll\Njust become corpses again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Hana will eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time the "Hitoyobashi" appeared\Nwas the year my grandpa was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandpa's sixty this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we make it longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to bring her back. I just\Nwant her to live as long as she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the best way to keep\Nher alive is to leave her as she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rid her of the "Mushi", can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but chances are nine out of\Nten that she will die on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think she's happy living as she is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We might as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to take such a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If she was alive at the time three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,she will return to normal after the "Hitoyobashi" appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling if or when such a thing would show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We have good arrangements for her if she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have them waiting any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't herself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's still being kept alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't treat her like a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll reinforce the bridge by the end of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you rest at my place for the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you living here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My family's in the village, but you know, I'm a pariah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been isolated from the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you ever thought about leaving by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a few times, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hana was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably leave after Hana's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So it finally collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because you crossed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's been using it lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, can you hurry up and fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's really busy though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hiding the Mushi-shi man, aren't\Nyou? We're not done talking yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a "Tanimodori" too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's more around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're Hana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,just forgotten everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to go near Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A black thread slipped out of her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Zen, do you want to leave with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Hitoyobashi" will show up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to cross it from this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's enough excited Nisekazura\Naround for even you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide by midnight tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling when you'll be able\Nto leave if you miss this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here. You've no regrets, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll fall through if you return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be able to forget if I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? We can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go forward. Hana's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Hana died three years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I survived these three years because\NHana was alive for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurt me to see her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was still better than now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't step on her and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to him since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, he probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time the Hitoyobashi\Nwill cross the valley again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,will be about twenty years from now.
